songs.title: Willy Wonka*
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Huh, bitch, ayy! Grrrr

[Chorus]
Diamond dog choker chain, that's a dogfight
Suck my dick like ice cream, what would you do for a Klondike?
They don't like me, huh, 'cause I'm icy, huh
Like I walked in Arby's and I bought a Hi-C
Mountain climbing cougar said she wanna hike me, huh
Willy Wonka clout goggles are so feisty
